<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title>Spirograph (in NodeJS and Python)</title>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css">
        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.plot.ly/plotly-latest.min.js"></script>
        <script type="text/javascript" async
          src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mathjax/2.7.1/MathJax.js?config=TeX-MML-AM_CHTML">
        </script>
        <script type="text/x-mathjax-config">
          MathJax.Hub.Config({tex2jax: {inlineMath: [['$','$'], ['\\(','\\)']]}});
          </script>
        <script src="assets/scripts.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="page-header text-center">
            <h1>Spirograph</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-4 text-center well well-sm">
                    <p>The spirograph equation for three or more wheels can be generalized as follows:</p>
                    <p>$$z(t) = \sum_{k=1}^n a_k e^{i2\pi(n_kt+\theta_k)}$$</p>
                    <p>This program solves those equations for three wheels, assuming all of the $a$ coefficients are 1 and $\theta$ coefficients are 0. Find more details online at <br/><a href="http://linuxgazette.net/133/luana.html">http://linuxgazette.net/133/luana.html</a></p>.
                    <form id="myForm" action="/" method="post">
                        <!-- use bootstrap's form-group class to fix spacing between inputs -->
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="n1">n1</label>
                            <input id="n1" type="text" name="n1" value="<%= data.inputs.n1 %>">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="n2">n2</label>
                            <input id="n2" type="text" name="n2" value="<%= data.inputs.n2 %>">
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="n3">n3</label>
                            <input id="n3" type="text" name="n3" value="<%= data.inputs.n3 %>">
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default">Calculate</button>
                    </form>
                    <div id="errors"></div>
                </div> <!-- col-sm-4 -->
                <div class="col-sm-8">
                    <div id="spirograph"></div>
                </div> <!-- col-sm-8 -->
            </div> <!-- row -->
        </div> <!-- container -->
    </body>
</html>
